+ On Guard 43 as Incorrect Quotes

> CONTEXT: I was bored this morning, and thought this would be a good idea. I am not known for my good ideas. 

> If you see these, Harry- I'm so sorry. Please forgive me for what I've done. Anyone else reading this - go look at [*https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/secure-facility-dossier-site-43 Site-43.] It's incredible, and full of heart and humour that never misses. And enjoy my silly drawings too, if you'd like! I've got way more on my [*https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/dr-vikki-lost Author Page]. :)
